==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Obstructionist
<hw>Ob*struc"tion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who deliberately
hinders progress; one who obstructs business, as in a legislative
body.</def> -- <def2><pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
obstructionists; causing obstruction; <as>as, <ex>obstructionist</ex>
tactics</as>.</def></def2> <mark>[Recent]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Obstructive</ent>⟦br⟧
